       >>>>>>>> Interaction forcing.
IFORCE 1 1 4 -10    0.1 1.0           [KB,KPAR,ICOL,FORCER,WLOW,WHIG]
IFORCE 1 1 5 -200  0.1 1.0            [KB,KPAR,ICOL,FORCER,WLOW,WHIG]
